text: Kristel Marbach (born 14 November 1988) is a Swiss volleyball player. She played at the 2013 Montreux Volley Masters, 2013 CEV Volleyball European Championship, and 2015 CEV Volleyball European Championship. She played for Volleyball Franches-Montagnes, Volley Köniz, and TSV Düdingen. == References == Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss volleyball players
